OL,2,MHigh-Power Rocketry on the Cheap
OL,4,CDanny Roberts
OL,5,CFri 14:30-15:10
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GRocketry is an expensive hobby. There
OL,9,Gare things you can do for cheap, but
OL,10,Gcutting costs too much can impact
OL,11,Gsafety, or more importantly: fun. This
OL,12,Gis a guide for how you can have as
OL,13,Gmuch fun as possible, as safely as
OL,14,Gpossible, without breaking the bank.
OL,15,GI'll take you through my journey
OL,16,Grunning an under-funded uni rocketry
OL,17,Gsociety, competing on <10% of the
OL,18,Gbudget of our peers, and later how I
OL,19,Gcontinued with the hobby on my own.
OL,20,GWe'll touch on materials,
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
